OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few showers possible today
OL,6,Fbut for many it will remain dry with
OL,7,Fbright and sunny spells breaking
OL,8,Fthrough the cloud. Strong northerly
OL,9,Fwinds near the coast, but lighter
OL,10,Ffurther inland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMostly dry but with an
OL,13,Fisolated shower possible. Late sunny
OL,14,Fspells in the evening, leading to
OL,15,Fclear spells overnight. Breezy near
OL,16,Fthe coast at first before easing later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
