OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA largely dry day with
OL,6,Fbright and sunny spells in the
OL,7,Fmorning. Turning cloudier through the
OL,8,Fafternoon with light rain spreading
OL,9,Feastwards in the evening. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMostly
OL,12,Fcloudy with heavy showers on Sunday.
OL,13,FDrier on Monday with sunny spells, the
OL,14,Fodd shower possible. Strong winds at
OL,15,Ftimes on Tuesday with rain clearing to
OL,16,Fheavy showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
